'''積遜·奇雲·史葛蘭特'''（{{lang-en|'''Jason Kelvin Scotland'''}}，{{bd|1979年|2月18日|catIdx=Scotland, Jason}}）出生於[[千里達及托巴哥|千里達及托巴哥]][[西班牙港|西班牙港]]以東的[[摩雲|摩雲]]（Morvant），是一名[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]。

==生平==
===球隊===
2007年5月[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]宣佈以2.5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]成功羅致史葛蘭特<ref name="swans">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6674397.stm|title=Swans sign Scotland from Saints|publisher=BBC Sport website|date=May 25, 2007|accessdate=2009-04-30|archive-date=2010-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100818212224/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6674397.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於7月4日獲得工作簽證後正式落實<ref name="permit">{{cite news|url=http://www.thecourier.co.uk/output/2007/07/05/sportstory9952444t0.asp|publisher=The Courier|title=Scotland makes move to Wales|author=Nicolson, Eric|date=July 5, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070709060119/http://www.thecourier.co.uk/output/2007/07/05/sportstory9952444t0.asp|archivedate=2007-07-09|accessdate=2009-04-30}}</ref>。8月11日首場披甲作客對[[奥尔德姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:奥特汉姆;zh-hk:奧咸}-]]即取得入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6931098.stm |title=Oldham 2-1 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-11 |accessdate=2009-07-25 |archive-date=2019-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918095233/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6931098.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，整季在各項比賽合共射入29球，成為[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]神射手，兼協助球隊贏得聯賽冠軍升級到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]，而他亦入選[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]。2008年8月19日在季末約滿的史葛蘭特同意與史雲斯續「長約」，合約年期未有透露<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4011354,00.html |title=Scotland commits to Swans |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-08-19 |accessdate=2009-07-25 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308011027/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4011354,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年3月2日史葛蘭特獲選為「2008年千里達及托巴哥足球先生」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://guardian.co.tt/sports/football/2009/03/02/scotland-mollon-ttff-s-2008-players-year |title=Scotland, Mollon—TTFF's 2008 'Players of the Year' |publisher=T&T Guardian |date=2009-03-02 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090303044129/http://guardian.co.tt/sports/football/2009/03/02/scotland-mollon-ttff-s-2008-players-year |archive-date=2009-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>，同年2月史葛蘭特6戰射入5球，獲選為「2月份英冠最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7934757.stm |title=Scotland named player of month |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-10 |accessdate=2009-07-25 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914191118/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7934757.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月10日聯賽主場1-0擊敗[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:普利茅斯;zh-hk:普利茅夫}-]]，史葛蘭特於77分鐘射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]，是他本季第21個入球，亦是加盟史雲斯以來第50個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7923092.stm |title=Swansea 1-0 Plymouth |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-10 |accessdate=2009-07-25 |archive-date=2019-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003230608/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7923092.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年7月9日史雲斯同意以200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]出售史葛蘭特到由前領隊馬天尼斯帶領的[[英超|英超]]球會[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]，交易於7月15日史葛蘭特成功申領工作簽證後正式落實<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5435157,00.html |title=Latics confirm Scotland capture |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-07-15 |accessdate=2009-07-16 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308041521/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5435157,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。惟在韋根的發展一直未如人意，上陣36場僅在聯賽及足總盃各入1球。

2010年8月23日史葛蘭特動筆簽約加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伊普斯维奇; zh-hk:葉士域治;}-]]，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期兩年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/8898247.stm |title=Jason Scotland finalises Ipswich Town switch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-23 |accessdate=2010-09-15 |archive-date=2019-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011180210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/8898247.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。翌日隨即在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第二圈作客對[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克魯]]於半場後補首次上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8936251.stm |title=Crewe 0-1 Ipswich |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-24 |accessdate=2010-09-15 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206040327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8936251.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；8月26日在聯賽回師主場迎戰[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布里斯托尔城; zh-hk:布里斯托城;}-]]，史葛蘭特正選上陣並射入加盟後首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8940425.stm |title=Ipswich 2-0 Bristol City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-26 |accessdate=2010-09-15 |archive-date=2019-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919184228/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8940425.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年4月3日史葛蘭特放棄合約列明的加薪權利爭取續約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17599809 |title=Jason Scotland waives Ipswich Town contract clause |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-04-03 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2012-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101182738/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17599809 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，終於7月6日獲提供一年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18736687 |title=Ipswich Town's Jason Scotland signs new one-year deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-07-06 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2012-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101182744/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18736687 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但自[[米克·麦卡锡|-{zh-hans:米克·麦卡锡; zh-hk:米克·麥卡菲;}-]]在11月上場後，僅獲1次後補上陣機會，在2013年1月21日與葉士域治同意提前解約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21123837 |title=Ipswich Town and Jason Scotland part company |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-01-21 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2013-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130124013608/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21123837 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年1月28日史葛蘭特以短約形式加盟另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]，為期至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21231286 |title=Jason Scotland: Barnsley sign former Ipswich Town striker |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-01-28 |accessdate=2013-05-15 |archive-date=2013-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130131140502/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/21231286 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間上陣20場射入6球，協助球隊成功保級，於2013年5月16日簽署一年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22553516 |title=Jason Scotland signs new Barnsley contract |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-05-16 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-date=2013-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617072319/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22553516 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
史葛蘭特被选入[[特立尼达和多巴哥|特立尼达和多巴哥]]队参加了[[2006年世界杯足球赛|2006年世界杯]]. 2008年10月8日在對[[多明尼加共和國國家足球隊|多明尼加]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.newsday.co.tt/sport/0,87760.html |title=Warriors destroy D/Republic 9-0 |publisher=T&T Newsday |date=2008-10-09 |accessdate=2009-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305033050/http://www.newsday.co.tt/sport/0,87760.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

